<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>FAKENING</title>

<style>


*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background: #a9c8a5;
}


.header{
    background:#b7d1b0;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:10px 20px;
}


.logo{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
}

.logo img{
    width:35px;
    height:35px;
}


.balay img{
    width:25px;
    cursor:pointer;
}


.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:800px;
    margin:40px auto;
    text-align:center;
}

.title{
    font-weight:bold;
    letter-spacing:3px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.subtitle{
    color:#333;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.faq{
    text-align:left;
}

.faq-item{
    background:#e6e6e6;
    margin:10px 0;
    padding:12px;
    border-radius:8px;
    cursor:pointer;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}


.faq-item span{
    font-weight:bold;
}


.faq-item:hover{
    background:#dcdcdc;
}


@media (max-width:600px){

    .title{
        font-size:18px;
    }

    .subtitle{
        font-size:14px;
    }

    .faq-item{
        font-size:14px;
        padding:10px;
    }
}

</style>
</head>

<body>


<div class="header">

    <div class="logo">
        
        <img src="hoplog.png" alt="lugo">
        <span>HopSearch</span>
    </div>

    <div class="balay">
        
        <img src="balay.png" alt="balay">
    </div>

</div>


<div class="container">

    <h2 class="title">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">
        These are the most commonly asked questions about HopSearch.<br>
        Happy to lend a helping hand!
    </p>

    <div class="faq">

        <div class="faq-item"><p>What is HopSearch?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Does HopSearch show which hospitals are currently available?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Can I filter facilities based on medical services offered?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Can I search for clinics and health centers, not just hospitals?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>How do I find the nearest hospital using HopSearch?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Why doesn't HopSearch show real-time bed availability or wait times?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>What information is shown for each medical facility?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Is HopSearch useful even when it's not an emergency?</p><span>+</span></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><p>Does HopSearch include both public and private facilities?</p><span>+</span></div>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
